                        <h1> the disadvantages of fog </h1>
                        <p> The disadvantages of fog computing center on its increased complexity, security vulnerabilities (like MitM attacks on more nodes), higher setup/management costs, potential for congestion, difficult scalability compared to the cloud, data consistency challenges, and higher power consumption due to the added infrastructure layer</p>
